You are correct, Dock Wharf Rat... I lost!<br><br>
I have finally realized that any effort expended to communicate any rational or logic to you is a wasted effort, truely a LOST cause.  Not that I am trying to force my ideas about the war in Viet Nam upon you...simply I am reacting to your dysfunctional, counter productive behavior in blaspheming the God whom I serve, the Nation that I serve and the countless patriots, living and dead, who have served, and still serve by my side.<br>
I have read so many chastizements of your inappropriate behavior on this site, all without any impact upon your self image of granduer.<br>
What kind of school did you graduate from?  Who would confer a doctorate upon someone of your poor vocabulary and low wit?  Did you buy a doctorate from one of those diploma factories?  Even if so, who in their right mind would allow someone of your level of bias and ignorance of therapy and theory, counsel anyone?  Do you seriously believe that your deportment is becoming of a mental health professional?  What kind of sickness do you harbor that provokes your never ending attacks upon respectable institutions and honorable people?  Why all the contempt?  Where is your sense of appreciation for being a free citizen in a free country?  Why do you not attempt to heal the wounds of traumatized veterans... instead of infecting their emotional wounds?<br>
Perhaps I am a loser in this instance.  I can not for the life of me understand why your vicious and erosive acts go unabated... a few decades ago you would have been shot to death for your treason.  Unfortunately, freedom is a concept that must operate within boundaries.  Freedom is not the total absence of boundaries. In the absence of boundaries you have anarchy, chaos and anything but a fertile ground where freedom can flourish.<br>
You are a fluttering cock roach in a beautiful bowl of soup!
